      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GETTING CHEEKY (1) is better than last start when fifth (20.92) in a TG1-4W at this track over 342m. Has ability and looks hard to stop. TIME OF DESIGN (5) has been in super consistent form, finishing in the minors at his last five runs. Last start finished 2nd over 342m at this track beaten half a length (19.93) behind Pink Poppy Club in a TG1-4W on March 31. Was a winner at his only start from this draw. Expecting another good run. CONNER'S RAIN (8) was on speed settling and found some traffic when checked, running on to finish third (20.37) at this track in a TG1-4W. Has the ability and can measure up. CERISE (7) warrants respect following a recent placing at big odds.",
